      <title>澳大利亚因涉嫌阿富汗战争罪剥夺其勋章</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/australia-strips-medals-over-alleged-war-crimes-in-afghanistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是 2020 年一份有关战争罪指控的报告的最新后果，澳大利亚将撤销少数在阿富汗部署期间担任指挥职务的士兵的军事奖励。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/australia-strips-medals-over-alleged-war-crimes-in-afghanistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:40:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>党内元老退却，日本领导人之争悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党领袖竞选于周四正式拉开帷幕，由于党内元老的控制力减弱，创纪录数量的候选人可以参与公开竞选，以带领国家度过关键的过渡时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/japan-s-leadership-race-is-wide-open-as-party-elders-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁经济复苏背后的推动者阿尔贝托·藤森去世，享年 86 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/alberto-fujimori-authoritarian-behind-peru-rebound-dies-at-86</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁前总统阿尔贝托·藤森去世，享年 86 岁。藤森曾监督击败毛派恐怖分子，控制了恶性通货膨胀，并在因参与行刑队杀人而入狱后继续在国家政治中占据重要地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/alberto-fujimori-authoritarian-behind-peru-rebound-dies-at-86</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国中东航母返航</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-11/us-aircraft-carrier-in-the-middle-east-is-heading-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——据美国官员称，五角大楼过去几周将两艘海军航空母舰保留在中东的罕见举措现已结束，西奥多·罗斯福号航空母舰正在回国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-11/us-aircraft-carrier-in-the-middle-east-is-heading-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰国索马里分支扩大影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/islamic-state-s-somalia-affiliate-expands-influence-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际危机组织指出，索马里伊斯兰国是全球恐怖组织在非洲之角的分支机构，其影响力通过调动资金向非洲大陆恐怖网络扩张而不断增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/islamic-state-s-somalia-affiliate-expands-influence-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国称朝鲜发射疑似弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-s-korea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国军方称，朝鲜周四凌晨在其东海岸发射了一枚疑似弹道导弹。几天前，朝鲜领导人金正恩誓言要大幅增强其核武器能力，并让军队做好战斗准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/n-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-s-korea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉因冈萨雷斯的支持威胁与西班牙断绝关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/venezuela-threatens-to-break-spain-ties-over-gonzalez-s-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙国会投票承认在 7 月份选举中挑战尼古拉斯·马杜罗的反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯为委内瑞拉当选总统后，委内瑞拉提议切断与马德里的外交关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/venezuela-threatens-to-break-spain-ties-over-gonzalez-s-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:09:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>敦促拜登重新考虑 140 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/biden-is-urged-to-reconsider-14-billion-us-steel-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司正在做最后的努力，争取对以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的支持，但该交易遭到总统乔·拜登、副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和前总统唐纳德·特朗普的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/biden-is-urged-to-reconsider-14-billion-us-steel-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 20:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因重复有关移民和宠物的谎言而面临强烈反击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-faces-blowback-for-online-lie-about-migrants-in-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普试图利用一个已被广泛揭穿的关于海地移民的网络谎言来攻击副总统卡马拉·哈里斯，但这对共和党候选人产生了反作用，成为他们第一次 — — 也可能是唯一一次 — — 辩论的标志性时刻之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/trump-faces-blowback-for-online-lie-about-migrants-in-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 18:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中情局官员因从事中国间谍活动被判入狱 10 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-11/ex-cia-officer-who-spied-for-china-faces-prison-time-and-a-lifetime-of-polygraph-tests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[檀香山（美联社）——一名前中央情报局官员兼联邦调查局合同语言学家因向中国从事间谍活动而收受现金、高尔夫球杆和其他昂贵礼物，于周三被判处 10 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-11/ex-cia-officer-who-spied-for-china-faces-prison-time-and-a-lifetime-of-polygraph-tests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 04:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
